1.title: Rogue One
1.plot: Jedi Council is an informative and internetaining talk show about all things Star Wars for fans or anyone curious about what's next in the Star Wars Universe. You can find new episodes airing every Thursday afternoon on YouTube by the people at Collider that bring you shows such as Movie Talk and Movie Trivia Schmoedown. The expert staff research the latest news about Star Wars so you don't have to. The show is done in segments such as a segment about Star Wars Canon (everything in the world of Star Wars as it relates to the movies) called 'What's the deal with Canon!...
